_sText:
This is my first map, i've taught myself how to use about everything, the advanced tools i looked up on google.com 
This map is complete with HDR lighting.  Planning on making another version of it gungame ready.   Its made for up to 16 players, and its basically a fancy square map.  There are ledges and shadow spots for campers and guns are laid out on the ground.

thanks for checking it out!
